race.comment: JUKEBOX LUCY (3) is unbeaten this campaign after two appearances, the latest win coming over 1100m at Mt Isa. Easy winner last time and looks the testing material again. REBELIOUS RED (9) finished tenth two runs back at Muswellbrook then improved last time out to score by a head over 1100m at Mudgee. Finds an easier race and can continue the winning form. INREADYNESS (5) was last at the races when he finished fourth over 1200m at Yeppoon on August 2. Among the better hopes while fresh. BORRELLI (7) ran below expectations last time at Rockhampton over 1050m, finishing seventh and beaten 8 lengths. Has good early toe so he should be handy in the run. Should give backers a sight.
